These are the sample metadata associated with EBI Study: ERP006059. In addition to the data available on the EBI website, we have included here Subject A's nutritional data. Each sample is associated with the previous day's nutrient intake, for days where those data were collected.
If you have further questions, please contact Lawrence David (l.d@duke.edu) or Eric Alm (ejalm@mit.edu).
